In the MATTER OF the ESTATE OF Anna FABICS. (Ellen Heine- Petitioner) C-715 September Term 2017
079927 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 23, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005576-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
